	<Title>
		Heel spurs: Do they always cause pain?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Heel spurs &amp;mdash; bony growths not necessarily the cause of your heel pain.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Do heel spurs always cause heel pain?
	</Question>
